{"tid":2368861,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【內地撈金】陳嘉佳轉攻內地做「吃播主」　賣命狂吃網民憂細細粒體重爆標","createTime":"2021-01-16T14:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T13:18:00.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"68fc7995e2127931889fa71820e8254d74336514","tid":2368861,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:30:36.000Z","msg":"有「細細粒」之稱的藝人陳嘉佳（小寶），近年轉簽為王祖藍旗下藝人後，轉為主攻內地市場。一向以體形龐大見稱的「細細粒」，最近更在抖音成為「吃播主」，表演瘋狂進食，可是有網友擔心其體重超標、影響健康。<br />\n<br />\n其實小寶陳嘉佳於2016年轉簽王祖藍旗下，慢慢亦把工作重心轉移內地。為配合內地市場，自然要開設微博及抖音帳號。「細細粒」更利用其體形以及愛吃的形象，在抖音當起「吃播主」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2850000/2852727/66802565_349330505999323_7168232047968727481_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2850000%2F2852727%2F66802565_349330505999323_7168232047968727481_n_600.jpg&h=83e13c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「吃播主」顧名思義，就是要在觀眾面前表演瘋狂進食，小寶除了是位吃播主，更會做「美食帶貨達人」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2850000/2852727/111_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2850000%2F2852727%2F111_600.jpg&h=850bf45d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小寶陳嘉佳以其名氣為廣告品牌宣傳推銷，其抖音已累積超過42萬粉絲追蹤。<br />\n<br />\n為吸引更多觀眾收看和買貨，小寶出盡法寶，比如為了推銷花膠，自言因為吃了15年花膠，所以臉上絕無皺紋。不過最令人震撼，是她即場鯨吞了4碗極難消化的花膠。"},{"pid":"8351b38507bbfd807a64282bb3491ab0cd45d41d","tid":2368861,"uid":231957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:31:59.000Z","msg":"who?"},{"pid":"b597114c308769c7fc26487b9b71243c8f67ef69","tid":2368861,"uid":168911,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:32:01.000Z","msg":"唔係禁止人暴食咩"},{"pid":"4c3be7b02d3196ff10e4f456e8cc35879569a541","tid":2368861,"uid":182127,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:34:39.000Z","msg":"自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425ee07b9ac52f4029b39c8687f72b73311319ca","tid":2368861,"uid":34470,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"b597114c308769c7fc26487b9b71243c8f67ef69","tid":2368861,"uid":168911,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:32:01.000Z","msg":"唔係禁止人暴食咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:34:41.000Z","msg":"因為呢啲只係佢正常嘅食量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76522265e3f5ddaee83fb58aaee64e90098180c2","tid":2368861,"uid":301050,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:34:45.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗咁作賤自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲衰過係TVB做配角"},{"pid":"b03ce4aa5f2c78024a939ea4a6a088cab183d1b3","tid":2368861,"uid":192409,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:35:51.000Z","msg":"無人同佢憂心 快撚啲食死佢"},{"pid":"8c448f7de3cd8c9ed2c709d0c0f2c75e8945e0e3","tid":2368861,"uid":326712,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"76522265e3f5ddaee83fb58aaee64e90098180c2","tid":2368861,"uid":301050,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:34:45.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗咁作賤自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲衰過係TVB做配角"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:37:56.000Z","msg":"佢係tvb做邊有可能有40幾萬傻鳩follow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朱千雪ig都係得60幾萬"},{"pid":"fa060e4cb5fbbfebe3aa2f2f8a42510a16e99c8b","tid":2368861,"uid":301050,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8c448f7de3cd8c9ed2c709d0c0f2c75e8945e0e3","tid":2368861,"uid":326712,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"76522265e3f5ddaee83fb58aaee64e90098180c2","tid":2368861,"uid":301050,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:34:45.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗咁作賤自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲衰過係TVB做配角"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:37:56.000Z","msg"